criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients confirmed in our hospital as having temporal lobe epilepsy and intending
             surgery to remove temporal lobe and hippocampal tissue;

          -  Volunteer to participate in this clinical trial, comply with the requirements of this
             clinical trial and sign an informed consent form.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic diseases of the central nervous system other than temporal lobe epilepsy;

          -  Other patients that are not suitable for this clinical trial determined by the
             researchers;
